Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.misc.lab_1

Class WheelOfFortune<T>

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.misc.lab_1.WheelOfFortune<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type yielded by get().
public class WheelOfFortune<T> extends Object
Wheel of Fortune class which will yield a value of T according to a probability distribution given by the set of events.

In order to pass all the unit tests, you will also have to implement code in FrequencyCounter. That bit of code is very simple.
